{"tid":1100112,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為手機爆炸，導致用家嚴重燒傷，網上消息已被官方封鎖","createTime":"2019-04-10T08:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:00:17.000Z","uid":155095,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2974051dcfed2147de29f6653f3e56af5183ba18","tid":1100112,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"中國網絡消息指，華為手機發生爆炸事故，導致用戶父親大腿嚴重燒傷。北京時間4月10日，中國多家財經網媒報道稱，4月1日，一名叫&ldquo;身體好虎&rdquo;的網友爆料，自己父親放在口袋裡的華為Nova3手機發生爆炸，導致大腿嚴重燒傷。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic4.dwnews.net/20190410/0d5c49520eeae632e7c615864426743c_w_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic4.dwnews.net%2F20190410%2F0d5c49520eeae632e7c615864426743c_w_m.jpg&h=e6b264c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為是中國一家高科技企業，在研發通信設備的同時，亦推出手機業務。華為因業務的高光表現，以及受到美國封殺而廣為人知。<br />\n<br />\n 4月1日，華為手機業務官微&ldquo;華為終端客服&rdquo;就回應稱，&ldquo;您的問題正在處理中，還請您耐心等待&rdquo;。 疑似華為手機產品線副總裁李小龍回應稱，自己不了解情況，但問題多出於用戶私自拆機和假冒電池所致。 李小龍還說，華為已推出補貼低價電池，就是想壓縮假冒電池的生存空間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic0.dwnews.net/20190410/4ea00e6c3ed6c22e80144e98bd413be8_w_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic0.dwnews.net%2F20190410%2F4ea00e6c3ed6c22e80144e98bd413be8_w_m.jpg&h=9d304d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於上述爆炸事故，李小龍透露已派專人處理。 不過，目前除一些截圖之外，&ldquo;身體好虎&rdquo;的爆料微博和其他財經媒體的報道均已被刪除，被指受華為公關所致。 <br />\n<br />\n此前，據媒體報道，華為手機內部已確定2019年目標，即趕超韓國企業三星，成為全球最大的智能手機制造廠商。 2018年底，華為常務董事、消費者業務CEO余承東表示，預計2019年華為手機出貨量超2.5億台，2020年將達到3億台。"},{"pid":"b5f64efbdce987fec625f70a9722105a6dc1d923","tid":1100112,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:20:59.000Z","msg":"房事龍.jpg"},{"pid":"68136c753939b9b31cb9fb8858ba40c3d0ca3aed","tid":1100112,"uid":63113,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:23:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEOEao6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEOEao6.png&h=aeecaab9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c972f8d85a07b90e06e6f3729f24fee882280ab","tid":1100112,"uid":170375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"終於有部會爆 <br />\n但華為：用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718358429631e1150e1048fe61f276ae9a17c2b5","tid":1100112,"uid":52062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:25:26.000Z","msg":"疑似華為手機產品線副總裁李小龍回應稱，自己不了解情況，但問題多出於用戶私自拆機和假冒電池所致。<br />\n<br />\n用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cac9db0f36a8c1c4c4f9d082f4f9c8f6ad99785","tid":1100112,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"爆炸? 好正常啫。中国喎"},{"pid":"0c145047cd9b3d80debdb345943ba1c0f176f44c","tid":1100112,"uid":223410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖"},{"pid":"03ddc0818fa512a9d0fc7f3575d7259ce5416bc2","tid":1100112,"uid":38729,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"完美複製三星技術"},{"pid":"70dc44dc05bb0ddad1c9e70a01abb7a43ef57616","tid":1100112,"uid":203417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:32:41.000Z","msg":"中國新兵器"},{"pid":"1496538ea02f358a6ee50406ff289eda14bc5fc5","tid":1100112,"uid":109383,"like":7,"dislike":19,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"03ddc0818fa512a9d0fc7f3575d7259ce5416bc2","tid":1100112,"uid":38729,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:30:19.000Z","msg":"完美複製三星技術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"離三星有一大段距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogvOOg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogvOOg2.png&h=9f767662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"492b91c9e63647b9df437030163ea9794268c46d","tid":1100112,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"話明 Nova"},